<p>
  <span class="nym">Remy</span>
  <span class="gen">m.</span>
  
  <span class="etym">A derivative of <span class="lang">Latin</span> <i>remex</i> 'oarsman'.
  </span>
  
</p>
  
<div class="usg">
  <p>The name of a 5th C saint, responsible for the baptism of Clovis and the conversion of the Franks to Christianity, as well as the name of an 8th C Frankish saint.</p>
</div>
  
  
<div class="def">
  <p>The name was most common in France.</p>
  
  


